data.description: Gorgeous 4 bed/2 bath home in Tillman Estates!  This home feels HUGE, with vaulted ceilings and lots of natural light throughout the open floorplan. Kitchen features granite counters, stainless appliances, pantry, island and a wrap-around breakfast bar. Spacious primary bedroom boasts an en-suite full bath with dual sinks, garden tub and walk-in closet. Backyard has been meticulously maintained, with mature landscaping and an extended covered patio, perfect for entertaining! AND double gates for RV parking!
